@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> [*]
Idle --> HourMode : press hour button
HourMode --> MinuteMode : press minute button
MinuteMode --> AlarmHourMode : press alarm hour button
AlarmHourMode --> AlarmMinuteMode : press alarm minute button
AlarmMinuteMode --> Idle : press hour button
AlarmMinuteMode --> HourMode : press minute button
AlarmMinuteMode --> MinuteMode : press alarm hour button
AlarmMinuteMode --> AlarmHourMode : press alarm minute button
Idle --> AlarmOnMode : press alarm on button
AlarmOnMode --> AlarmOffMode : press alarm off button
AlarmOffMode --> Idle : press alarm on button
AlarmOnMode --> AlarmOffMode : press alarm off button
AlarmOffMode --> AlarmOnMode : press alarm off button
Idle --> LightOnMode : press light button
LightOnMode --> LightOffMode : button released
LightOffMode --> Idle : button pressed
@enduml
